""
WITH order_product_pairs AS (
  SELECT
    oi1.order_id,
    oi1.product_id AS product_id_1,
    oi2.product_id AS product_id_2
  FROM order_items oi1
  JOIN order_items oi2
    ON oi1.order_id = oi2.order_id
    AND oi1.product_id < oi2.product_id
),
product_pairs AS (
  SELECT
    op.order_id,
    p1.product_name AS product_a,
    p2.product_name AS product_b
  FROM order_product_pairs op
  JOIN products p1
    ON op.product_id_1 = p1.product_id
  JOIN products p2
    ON op.product_id_2 = p2.product_id
),
co_purchase_counts AS (
  SELECT
    product_a,
    product_b,
    COUNT(*) AS co_purchase_count
  FROM product_pairs
  GROUP BY product_a, product_b
  ORDER BY co_purchase_count DESC
  LIMIT 2
)
SELECT * FROM co_purchase_counts;
""

""
SELECT
    strftime('%Y-%m', orders.order_date) AS month,
    categories.category_name,
    AVG(order_items.quantity) AS avg_units_sold
FROM
    orders
JOIN
    order_items ON orders.order_id = order_items.order_id
JOIN
    products ON order_items.product_id = products.product_id
JOIN
    categories ON products.category_id = categories.category_id
WHERE
    categories.category_name LIKE 'Bikes%'
GROUP BY
    month,
    categories.category_name
ORDER BY
    month,
    categories.category_name;
""

""
WITH user_expenditure AS (
  SELECT
    o.customer_id,
    SUM(oi.quantity * p.price) AS total_expenditure
  FROM
    orders o
    JOIN order_items oi ON o.id = oi.order_id
    JOIN products p ON oi.product_id = p.id
  GROUP BY
    o.customer_id
)
SELECT
  c.first_name || ' ' || c.last_name AS user_name,
  ue.total_expenditure
FROM
  user_expenditure ue
  JOIN customers c ON ue.customer_id = c.id
ORDER BY
  ue.total_expenditure DESC
LIMIT 5
""
